pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Plant Vitamin D 40ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Vegan source of vitamin D3 derived from marine algae to
support a healthy immune system and bone health.

Wanderlust Plant Vitamin D3 is a
consciously created, vegan source of vitamin D3 in a convenient, readily absorbed liquid spray. Vitamin D is an important vitamin that plays a
role in supporting healthy immune function, maintaining bone health and assisting the absorption of dietary calcium.

Size: 40 mL

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should
not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

EACH SPRAY (180 MICROLITRES)
CONTAINS:
Colecalciferol 25 micrograms
Equiv. vitamin D3 1000 IU

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours.
Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One spray (180 microlitres) into the
mouth once daily, or as directed by
your healthcare practitioner. Shake well
before use.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is missing or broken.
